  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0daf \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0db6\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf - \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The letter of resignation will be given today - President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mr. Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena said that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa contacted him on the phone and announced that he will resign from his post today.",
        "Accordingly, the Speaker said that the President announced that the letter in this regard will be given to him today.",
        "Accordingly, the Speaker said that a President will be appointed on the 20th of this month and the people are requested to work peacefully until then."
      ],
